description	"T3-M4

Class: Super Battle Droid
Brief Overview: 
A fast moving support class with a weapon-disabling ion blaster and a freeze ray. 

^2Weaponry:
- Mounted Blaster (Based on SBD Arm Blaster 0)
- Ion Blaster
-- Based on Clone Pistol (1)
-- Electrocutes targets

^8Attributes:
- Damage taken ignores locational differences
- Self-Repair (Armor Regen 1)
- Fast Hacking
- Radar Scanner (Passive Force Sense 1)
- Battery Recharge (3)

^3Abilities:
- Low Power Mode ^3[CS1]
- Cryoban Projector ^3[CS2]

Originally built as a code-slicing droid, and outfitted with numerous weapon attachments for criminal purposes on the planet Taris, T3-M4 was acquired by the amnestic Revan by chance before narrowly escaping the planet's devastation at the hands of Darth Malak. T3-M4 would prove a loyal companion and invaluable asset to Revan and later to the Jedi Exile Meetra Surik."